contents.value: Baby was alert and active. She can move the walker backwards. OS and Mom talked about the dangers of a walker. She is eating 1 tablespoon of rice in every 4 oz bottler ever 4 hours. She eats baby food. Sweet potato broke out her face and made red spots on her body. Mom does not plan to feed her any more sweet potatoes. She has over 8 wet diapers and 1 bowel movement every day. She takes 2-3 naps in the day and sleeps 4-5 hours at night before waking to eat. OS Melinda Hill
